{"tid":166771,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"高鐵一地兩檢問題","createTime":"2017-03-22T11:23:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-24T11:22:56.000Z","uid":12614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8d93ed225f2ad150edc2066ef76d398cdbbf3946","tid":166771,"uid":12614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T11:23:01.000Z","msg":"想問下點解高鐵唔可以好似火車咁兩地兩檢，去到廣州先做檢查<br />\n<br />\n另外想問紅磡火車做到無人係落車途中偷走？係咪去到廣州零零舍舍有個月台for 旅客？"},{"pid":"c2d7236d4aff434e560ada4611a87c89f716fd18","tid":166771,"uid":12614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T11:26:59.000Z","msg":"Hel"},{"pid":"2bdef3c1e0a88b5f4364b1f4a11a4ffea35edcd5","tid":166771,"uid":57462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T11:27:15.000Z","msg":"變左低鐵"},{"pid":"eec51ca890ad8fa752acc0cca5e4729c48172926","tid":166771,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T11:31:54.000Z","msg":"土地割據鐵路"},{"pid":"e23b90b087374887241efacd1c81d6ae8195eef5","tid":166771,"uid":12614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T11:34:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>土地割據鐵路</blockquote><br />\nMore"},{"pid":"336b74c15c7317b82cf2d1f11c145e4016b2f0cb","tid":166771,"uid":22313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T11:38:41.000Z","msg":"根本無必要要起高鐵直通<br />\n識好多大陸人，有啲係大學教授級，都覺得香港咁閪細起直通高鐵嚟把撚，咁多年嚟過關之後轉大巴/火車/高鐵都無問題"},{"pid":"8baca0cbba560c58475f15c59ddf4b1394d47129","tid":166771,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T11:54:01.000Z","msg":"因為佢哋唔想去香港要分車卡<br />\n<br />\n依家北京落九龍都要分卡，佢要做到唔分卡去到香港落車先當出境。"},{"pid":"bd16adcd0a5dd823796918103410a4355646ae42","tid":166771,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T11:55:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>根本無必要要起高鐵直通<br />\n識好多大陸人，有啲係大學教授級，都覺得香港咁閪細起直通高鐵嚟把撚，咁多年嚟過關之後轉大巴/火車/高鐵都無問題</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n根本就應該深圳福田站做出境，要落香港。<br />\n<br />\n一日真係咁多車落香港咩。"},{"pid":"f199a18bccc2d9d9111d5dbc461b26d28ec5d301","tid":166771,"uid":68094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T11:57:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a7a13b0536f4df7b0ed84ca1e33a7755a84199af","tid":166771,"uid":49643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T12:08:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想問下點解高鐵唔可以好似火車咁兩地兩檢，去到廣州先做檢查<br />\n<br />\n另外想問紅磡火車做到無人係落車途中偷走？係咪去到廣州零零舍舍有個月台for 旅客？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n成個中國咁多高鐵站，邊有可能每個站都為你set入境/海關<br />\n<br />\n紅磡&lt;&gt;廣州（中間仲有個常平站）係有個專用月台係禁區，一落車就上大堂排隊過關"},{"pid":"5753e36f078a300d45991b2fa7192e6f0d1c1f51","tid":166771,"uid":50658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T12:12:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想問下點解高鐵唔可以好似火車咁兩地兩檢，去到廣州先做檢查<br />\n<br />\n另外想問紅磡火車做到無人係落車途中偷走？係咪去到廣州零零舍舍有個月台for 旅客？</blockquote><br />\n唔可以兩地兩檢根本就係政府自己唔想做<br />\n一路都係話用咗咁多錢冇理由仲兩地兩檢為理由去堅持要一地兩檢"},{"pid":"aa1f204bf582400444824e0ca139e8d4f885acf0","tid":166771,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T12:13:45.000Z","msg":"因為佢唔只shuttle你上廣州禁區入境囉"},{"pid":"6e4ef5fe7b146b9aba16624e616d161dc71929cb","tid":166771,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T12:14:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>因為佢唔止shuttle你上廣州禁區入境囉</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3e39bfb44f7b4bc56df210e53efe5e1c64642f4","tid":166771,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T12:18:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>想問下點解高鐵唔可以好似火車咁兩地兩檢，去到廣州先做檢查<br />\n<br />\n另外想問紅磡火車做到無人係落車途中偷走？係咪去到廣州零零舍舍有個月台for 旅客？</blockquote><br />\n唔可以兩地兩檢根本就係政府自己唔想做<br />\n一路都係話用咗咁多錢冇理由仲兩地兩檢為理由去堅持要一地兩檢</blockquote><br />\n個問題係咩站做, 因而畀咩服務落香港"},{"pid":"25715b2f91db960b0a83646e81dc9c74c982097c","tid":166771,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T12:29:59.000Z","msg":"50年效益係 870億呀～～<br />\n<br />\n主要計乘客節省嘅時間，即係點？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/22/202832_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F22%2F202832_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=52c52e6c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fb60799a72cfd0887b0be6ae5b565db9874cf3d1","tid":166771,"uid":43633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T12:33:06.000Z","msg":"支那唔可以起香港執法"},{"pid":"23e1842e3a25108f32eacc8792fdfb27dea4889c","tid":166771,"uid":41116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T12:35:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>根本無必要要起高鐵直通<br />\n識好多大陸人，有啲係大學教授級，都覺得香港咁閪細起直通高鐵嚟把撚，咁多年嚟過關之後轉大巴/火車/高鐵都無問題</blockquote><br />\n一路都話攞舊錢擴闊東鐵好過<br />\n搞d 直達線"},{"pid":"5795f390266665fbd9916ae1fd01a3eefebf11ef","tid":166771,"uid":50658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T13:36:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>50年效益係 870億呀～～<br />\n<br />\n主要計乘客節省嘅時間，即係點？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/22/202832_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F22%2F202832_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=52c52e6c&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n原來時間真係金錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"899e8ac7db6aeeba710716b3bbd7ccbca5d4c90a","tid":166771,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T14:03:03.000Z","msg":"想快，同埋政治因素，令香港慢慢推大陸法"},{"pid":"2211a5c83be6c43fa835a8282eafb8f517254275","tid":166771,"uid":8257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T14:06:09.000Z","msg":"on9 高鐵一地兩檢根本係偽命題 佢起黎根本係軍用同將香港變成香港市用"},{"pid":"6bcc65f8ced5e1c0874868a10fa6b15b11b7d8d8","tid":166771,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T11:22:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 